{"tid":1401393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線 係你哋自己有份當前線condom呀！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:13.000Z","uid":76543,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31944aa517f72a4c48fb17e71a584828f8eae649","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"今日下晝大家都覺得be water做得好好<br />\n夜晚點解又要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重蹈覆轍</strong></span></span>呀<br />\n次次戀戰 次次都有手足俾人捉<br />\n好多手足可以犧牲 我哋原意明明係一個都唔想犧牲呀<br />\n唔洗屌我冷氣軍師啦 我都上過前線<br />\n前線都係抗爭一部分 唔係我哋行頭話事權就大啲呀<br />\n咩唔係前線就唔好咁多嘢講<br />\n我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係分化</strong></span></span><br />\n但係我哋爭取緊一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主社會</strong></span></span> 咁係咪應接納多方意見呀<br />\n好多提你哋 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>be water 不易戀戰</strong></span></span><br />\n你哋就屌 知唔知一場運動最易失敗嘅原因會係咩呀 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係互屌呀</span></strong></span><br />\n真真正正撚一次狗 be一次water好唔好呀<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔想再有手足被捕啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"1e7a3ed754f1ea9693a85e1d3ec9efe07ce6c857","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:43:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"67feb81b4eceb0594d0ff7b14f352b03e8bc2748","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"b161e102eb0757c53d000032dd9a1ee3076ddbbb","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"85罷工"},{"pid":"adbff606a9292b8a0fd075ac465054cc9bf4ca0c","tid":1401393,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n前線有鬼？？？有勇無謀？？？唔知真假<br />\n我懷疑有狗混入 叫大家留係到<br />\n已經講左成個禮拜be water<br />\n唔好理佢地 現場要走快d走<br />\n去咩黃大仙 狗要追上你可以好快<br />\n唔好慢慢行 要跑！！！！地鐵巴士都得</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8b9b0472f9cbc8ab482cb2f9d9b8152c333d142","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"85 罷工"},{"pid":"cca0ab4c3e586c2ebea2ceeb76434c1b2c53ad21","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能再少呀！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c7c6bf1997783e7f451f74ce8bc83f43d4f93df","tid":1401393,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67ccd3391a32b698f5f8b9e27d7d4f8f6e4d125a","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"前線 你哋為香港抗爭緊 背負住香港人嘅稱號 有責任保護身邊手足架"},{"pid":"f6afec576c6a027f63a17fe00077d4b703425606","tid":1401393,"uid":26813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sorry借位宣傳<br />\n幫手推俾前線手足睇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［前線路障快閃團］簡易快速拆鐵欄攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a36dd28d9cf8509e96c16412b541732692b3da7","tid":1401393,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bd4f26713f8411e56b75acc32bc213c66b9e85","tid":1401393,"uid":7654